videos.description: Quade Green, Kassius Robertson, and Shai Gilgeous-Alexander all drain 3-pointers for Kentucky.
videos.headline: Kentucky hits three triples in a row

videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander lobs it up to PJ Washington who hammers home the alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Washington shows no mercy at the rim

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo takes the ball to the rim in transition and hammers home a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Diallo's posterizing slam for Kentucky

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo drives into the paint and finds Jarred Vanderbilt who throws down the hammer.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Vanderbilt gets a dunk in transition
